title: 07/26/2021 - HOUR 3 - Rodgers, Deshaun
itunes:title: 07/26/2021 - HOUR 3 - Rodgers, Deshaun
description:
In this hour of The Herd with Colin Cowherd, Doug Gottlieb--in for Colin--explains why Green Bay quarterback Aaron Rodgers has no real leverage in Green Bay because of his contract. Plus, John Middlekauff of the "3 and Out" podcast joins The Herd to chat about quarterbacks Aaron Rodgers and Deshaun Watson as well as other NFL matters.
